This is for the little servo tester I rigged up.

I'm loosely following: 

http://learn.adafruit.com/controlling-a-servo-with-a-beaglebone-black/installing-the-python-library

The beaglebone I'm using at the moment is labeled "4"


Setting up Adafruit io python library:




opkg update && opkg install python-pip python-setuptools python-smbus
pip install Adafruit_BBIO
